text: Werethekau is an Egyptian Goddess, credited with supernatural powers. The name weret hekau means "great of magic".Barbara S. Lesko, The great goddesses of Egypt, University of Oklahoma Press, 1999, p 74 Werethekau was the god of protection magic, and was often seen with Isis and Ra in the carvings. ==References== Category:Egyptian gods and goddesses
title: Werethekau
